{"tid":1775652,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔唔知係咪因為天氣凍食少左野","createTime":"2019-12-09T03:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T14:07:20.000Z","uid":240448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0dac49ea5d17f2f4df389a502de35b7f8ca23b68","tid":1775652,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n你地家中毛小孩有無因為最近天氣凍左食少左野係咁訓？ <br />\n<br />\n呢個係我屋企細佬第一個冬天 <br />\n佢平時天氣暖食量都幾大<br />\n但呢幾日凍左咁多 食少左野 係平時既3分1 <br />\n又係咁訓 都有同哥哥玩 但成日都曚曚鬆鬆咁<br />\n<br />\n2個幾月前領養佢番屋企時 已經身體檢查左 身體無問題<br />\n呢2日只係見佢眼屎多左 唔知係咪感冒？ 但又無鼻涕或者嘔。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: orange;\">已經book左聽日去睇醫生 </span></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81326750ef763af2ef48e8ea7517207fcef86093","tid":1775652,"uid":44562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"我個兩隻冬天食多咗好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd04131fffbd35642ea09a630d2547acf0a9953","tid":1775652,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81326750ef763af2ef48e8ea7517207fcef86093","tid":1775652,"uid":44562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"我個兩隻冬天食多咗好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"我屋企哥哥都係食多左<br />\n<br />\n就係細佬食少左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩事"},{"pid":"664f7d0806527d547689991d6b4d0645589559ed","tid":1775652,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"有冇試下唔同嘅食物 ?"},{"pid":"d019502ba2826081f33db110b4ce552451981d4f","tid":1775652,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664f7d0806527d547689991d6b4d0645589559ed","tid":1775652,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"有冇試下唔同嘅食物 ?"},"citedBy":0,